Developer Terms of Use
des: eFriend Interactive Journal changes the traditional journaling experience. The eFriend Interactive Journal skill allows users to log journal entries of emotions and receive fun, therapeutic activity suggestions. Users can also retrieve their prior emotion logs. Although the research behind eFriend Interactive Journal is based on psychological evidence, this skill is not meant to replace a therapist or give professional mental health advice. To use the skill, simply say, "Alexa, open Interactive Journal."
